::  Tests for bitcoin-spv library
::  Generated from real Bitcoin testnet blocks
::  100 test cases collected via automated testing
::
::  TEST-DRIVEN DEVELOPMENT APPROACH:
::  1. Baseline tests (commented out) verified current behavior:
::     - 50 cases produce wrong hashes
::     - 50 cases produce correct hashes
::  2. Goal: Fix hash computation so ALL 100 cases produce correct hashes
::  3. Current tests verify this goal - they will fail until we fix the bug
::  4. Suspected bug: byte order issue in parse-fixed-hex using `can` which reverses bytes
::
/+  *test, bitcoin-spv
=,  bitcoin-spv
